/*       MD057289 - There is inconsistency with migration script     */
/*                  SMUC00032 and GL0600 processing for newly opened */
/*                  accounts                                         */
/*                - Clear PRFC value if Analytical Accounting is ON. */
/*       MD046248 - Finastra Rebranding                              */
/*       BG26993 - Delivery of upgrade programs to core.             */
/*               - Renamed S248369C01.                               */
/*       248369  - Update ACCNTAB to complete fix SC248369.          */
